data.description: Charming Madrona Beach home with amazing VIEWS of the Saratoga Passage with PRIVATE BEACH access just 2 blocks away! No ferry island with kayaking, hiking trails, fishing and crabbing! Island living at its best! This 2-bedroom (plus bonus room with closet), 2 bath home features a spacious kitchen with island and sea glass tile backsplash, engineered wood floors, gas fireplace and radiant tile floors in bathrooms! Plenty of outdoor entertaining space with covered gazebo, outdoor movie theatre and wireless speakers. Fully fenced yard with multiple view decks, mature landscaping and newer vinyl garden shed. Perfect for everyday living, beach house or vacation rental! Come enjoy what Camano Island has to offer!
